  "detailed_description": "Embark on your adventures in the fantastical land of Tainuote. <br>The mystical power of tarot will guide you to eradicate evil and darkness after your reincarnation. <br>To be a great warrior, to increase your strength, to explore the unknown, to give you infinite joy.<br>A Rougelike turn-based FTB game.<br><br>The game is a full roguelike experience, with lots of fun to build, strengthen, explore, and collect<br>In-game language switch, if necessary, please set in the game<br>Adventurers! Roll your dice! Let the unknown fantasy adventure begin!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/f904b55290243b45b8f1cc38e74e65fa.avif?t=1703102259\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>features<br>Adopt the way of dice movement + slot machine reward, make the adventure full of infinite fun unknown,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game includes collection, enhancement, building, tower climbing and other Rougelike gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Combat using FTB turn-based combat mode, with a variety of buffs to enhance combat fun<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/8fd04addd28766b4cda1ca43c856cf92.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/8fd04addd28766b4cda1ca43c856cf92.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/8fd04addd28766b4cda1ca43c856cf92.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Embark on your adventures in the fantastical land of Tainuote. <br>The mystical power of tarot will guide you to eradicate evil and darkness after your reincarnation. <br>To be a great warrior, to increase your strength, to explore the unknown, to give you infinite joy.<br>A Rougelike turn-based FTB game.<br><br>The game is a full roguelike experience, with lots of fun to build, strengthen, explore, and collect<br>In-game language switch, if necessary, please set in the game<br>Adventurers! Roll your dice! Let the unknown fantasy adventure begin!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/f904b55290243b45b8f1cc38e74e65fa.avif?t=1703102259\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br>features<br>Adopt the way of dice movement + slot machine reward, make the adventure full of infinite fun unknown,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/c5d112ef45cff4eab5a89d6759ab450c.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game includes collection, enhancement, building, tower climbing and other Rougelike gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7efbab07420a877da2f458e3776c8552.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/176f7a1d4ec77cf2cd6aee454b01a807.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.webm?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/7a84dfe2f118b0824ea95d01cd76c2bb.mp4?t=1703102259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Combat using FTB turn-based combat mode, with a variety of buffs to enhance combat fun<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/8fd04addd28766b4cda1ca43c856cf92.poster.avif?t=1703102259\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957620/extras/8fd04a